name: Romantic Poetry and Prose
description: Poetry and critical prose of Blake, W. Wordsworth, Coleridge, Byron, P.B. Shelley, Keats; may include brief selections from other writers such as Crabbe, Dorothy Wordsworth, Scott, Landor, Mary Shelley, Clare, De Quincey. [72L]
prerequisites: 1.0 credit in ENG and 3.0 additional credits.
